data.description: This charming property is located in a picturesque rural setting and boasts two parcels of land totaling 5.8 acres. The house features 2 bedrooms and 1 bath with an extra room that could be used as a den or office. It has a 2 car carport and a private patio. The immediate surroundings of the property have been fenced and additionally, there is a greenhouse to grow your own vegetables, there is also room for your chicken. The possibilities are limitless. The house sits in a parcel with  2 acres and the other parcel next to this one has 3.8 acres and a building that creates the possibility of having an additional home. Buyers are encouraged to make all necessary investigations about the possibilities for this property. Price correction come and take advantage of it!!! Sellers are motivated
